description:
Description

This is litle batch game where you can make your own maps or play ohter players  made maps.

Download link: https://bit.ly/3Wcfrr9

Unzip archive and start playing!

Message for n00bs: This game is not a virus. I have checked game source code and this doesn't have any virus commands.

Links:

Blog: http://markusmaal.blogspot.com
Google+ : http://google.com/+MarkusMaal

comments.text:
Didn't work as it should but...
Awesome! I am trying to create a mix of text-based and "platform" adventure, I must tell it will help me a lot.
today I just have a fake loading bar, 1 NPC, simple battle system and exp (lvl up system comming not so soon)

BTW dude... There's a lot of command lines, must have taken years to do that!
